						               													<description>This intensely fun and spooky card game is based off the hit series &amp;quot;Skeleton Creek&amp;quot; by Patrick Carman. Just like the books, you must gather your friends and hunt for the ghost of Old Joe Bush! Be cunning, be careful and explore the mystery of Skeleton Creek...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game starts with 4 cards being dealt to each player face down...one of the cards (placed randomly) is the Old Joe Bush card! At the start of every turn a player draws a card, they may then choose to play a card, but at the end of each turn a player may only have 4 cards in their hand. Each player must also leave their cards face down until it their turn. The game ends when the last card from the draw pile is taken. From there, each player (including the one that drew the last card) takes their last turn. The object of the game is to end with Old Joe Bush in your hand!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use Night Vision to peek at another player's hand. Use Ryan's Journal to take the top card off of a player's hand. There are countless possibilities and strategies to use to capture the Ghost of Old Joe Bush!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
